```plantuml
@startuml solenya-group_solenya

actor Developer

participant "App" as App
participant "Component" as Component
participant "Router" as Router
participant "Storage" as Storage
participant "TimeTravel" as TimeTravel
participant "Validator" as Validator

Developer -> App: Initialize application
App -> Component: Instantiate root component
Component -> Component: Manage state
Component -> Validator: Validate component data
Validator -> Component: Return validation results
Component -> Component: Render view with state
Component -> "Virtual DOM": Perform diff and patch
Component -> Router: Navigate to new route
Router -> Component: Load new component
Component -> Storage: Serialize state
Storage -> Component: Return persisted state
Component -> TimeTravel: Save state for time travel
TimeTravel -> Component: Enable stepping through states
Developer -> Component: Trigger update
Component -> Component: Update state
Component -> "Virtual DOM": Perform diff and patch

@enduml
```